definition.value:
The nationality of the patient. should be a country code from ISO 3166-1 code system

Example:
~~~
{
   "url":"http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/patient-nationality",
   "extension": [
   {
      "url":"code",
      "valueCodeableConcept":{
         "coding": [
         {
            "system":"urn:iso:std:iso:3166",
            "code":"NO"
         }
      ]
      }
      }
   ]
}
~~~
